  <brief_title>Pelvic Floor Symptoms After Bilateral Sacrospinous Fixation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pelvic Floor Symptoms and Patients´ Satisfaction After Bilateral Sacrospinous Fixation for the Primary Treatment of Pelvic Organ Prolapse ICS-POPQ Stage IV: A Prospective Observational Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
