  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to the assessment of pelvic floor symptoms and patients´ satisfaction after
      bilateral sacrospinous fixation for the primary treatment of pelvic organ prolapse stage IV.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
